The package boost-numeric-conversion is compatible with built-in CMake targets of FindBoost.cmake:

    find_package(Boost REQUIRED COMPONENTS numeric_conversion)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::numeric_conversion)

or the generated cmake configs via:

    find_package(boost_numeric_conversion REQUIRED CONFIG)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::numeric_conversion)
